<h3 id="Task-3:-Data-Standardisation">Task 3: Data Standardisation<a class="anchor-link" href="#Task-3:-Data-Standardisation">¶</a></h3><p>Before combining datasets or performing analysis, categorical columns must be standardized.</p>
<p>The following steps were performed:</p>
<ol>
<li>Removed extra spaces from text columns using str.strip().</li>
<li>Converted text values to lowercase to avoid case differences.</li>
<li>Standardized old state names:<ul>
<li>Orissa → Odisha</li>
<li>Uttaranchal → Uttarakhand</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Checked and removed duplicate rows.</li>
<li>Verified that state names, crop names, district names, and season names follow a consistent format.</li>
</ol>
<p>These steps improve data quality and prevent incorrect grouping, filtering, and merging results.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
