</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput" data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<ol>
<li><p>State names contained formatting inconsistencies such as extra spaces, mixed capitalization, and old state names.</p>
</li>
<li><p>These inconsistencies were corrected using trimming, lowercase conversion, and state-name replacement.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Duplicate rows were identified and removed.</p>
</li>
<li><p>After cleaning, duplicate counts became zero and the datasets were ready for reliable merging.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
