<div class="jp-Cell jp-MarkdownCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=736296ae-86a0-496a-8c77-046cfa8a2453">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea"><div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput" data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<h2 id="What-I-Did-and-Why-It-Worked">What I Did and Why It Worked<a class="anchor-link" href="#What-I-Did-and-Why-It-Worked">¶</a></h2><p><strong>Method used:</strong> IQR — because it is not affected by the extreme
values we are trying to find. Mean and standard deviation are
both pulled by outliers so they are not reliable for this task.</p>
<p><strong>What was found:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A small number of rows had AQI below 0 — these were deleted
because a negative AQI is physically impossible</li>
<li>Some values were far above the upper IQR fence — these were
capped at the fence value, not deleted, because extreme
pollution does genuinely happen and we do not want to
remove real events from the data</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Proof it worked:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The maximum AQI dropped after capping</li>
<li>The mean came down closer to the median</li>
<li>The after histogram shows a cleaner right side with
no extreme long tail stretching far to the right</li>
<li>The standard deviation is smaller meaning the data
is now less spread out and more consistent</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="jp-Cell jp-MarkdownCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=34b02483-527b-46ab-b1ed-fd99385cf918">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea"><div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput" data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<h2 id="Lab-2">Lab 2<a class="anchor-link" href="#Lab-2">¶</a></h2><h2 id="Data-exploration-and-inferences">Data exploration and inferences<a class="anchor-link" href="#Data-exploration-and-inferences">¶</a></h2><h2 id="Task-6--Is-India's-Air-Getting-Better-or-Worse-Over-Time?">Task 6  Is India's Air Getting Better or Worse Over Time?<a class="anchor-link" href="#Task-6--Is-India's-Air-Getting-Better-or-Worse-Over-Time?">¶</a></h2><p>The Date column is currently stored as plain text.
Before I can group anything by year, I need to convert it
into a proper date format. Once that is done I can pull out
just the year and calculate the average AQI for each year.</p>
<p>I will use a line chart because it is the clearest way to
show how something changes over time. Even someone who has
never seen data before can read a line going up or down.</p>
<p>I will also mark the worst year and best year on the chart
so the journalist can see them immediately without looking
at a table of numbers.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs" id="cell-id=1156c566-c197-43f9-9dbb-a7acbb3408b7">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [77]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pandas</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nn">pd</span>

<span class="n">aqi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read_csv</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"city_day.csv"</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs" id="cell-id=f23f18a7-5dc1-484d-93e5-0cc3fac37624">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [78]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># the date column is text right now</span>
<span class="c1"># convert it to a proper date so we can work with it</span>

<span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Date"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">to_datetime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Date"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">errors</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"coerce"</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs" id="cell-id=2cb5fa0a-3aa3-47a6-82ce-50f1c6bbf898">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [79]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># pull out just the year from the date</span>

<span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Date"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">dt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">year</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs" id="cell-id=398765a1-7d1c-4da7-8d77-7a26a29a89a2">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [80]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># remove rows where AQI or Year is missing</span>

<span class="n">aqi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">aqi</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">dropna</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">subset</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"AQI"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">])</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs" id="cell-id=319c2cac-730f-4b83-9da7-23f115c8d4c9">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [81]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># keep only 2015 to 2023</span>

<span class="n">aqi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">2015</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">aqi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">aqi</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="mi">2023</span><span class="p">]</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=5be64927-81aa-43c1-84bf-00c07ba9b0db">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [82]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># find average AQI for each year</span>

<span class="n">yearly</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">aqi</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">groupby</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">)[</span><span class="s2">"AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">reset_index</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">yearly</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">columns</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="jp-Cell-outputWrapper">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-OutputCollapser jp-Cell-outputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-OutputArea jp-Cell-outputArea">
<div class="jp-OutputArea-child">
<div class="jp-OutputPrompt jp-OutputArea-prompt"></div>
<div class="jp-RenderedText jp-OutputArea-output" data-mime-type="text/plain" tabindex="0">
<pre>   Year  Average_AQI
0  2015        212.5
1  2016        197.2
2  2017        181.5
3  2018        182.7
4  2019        156.5
5  2020        113.5
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=007b09c5-bd8c-413f-843e-28e17ef9a25c">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [83]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># find the worst and best year</span>

<span class="n">worst</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">yearly</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">loc</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">idxmax</span><span class="p">()]</span>
<span class="n">best</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">yearly</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">loc</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">idxmin</span><span class="p">()]</span>

<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Most polluted year :"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]),</span>
      <span class="s2">"— AQI"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Least polluted year:"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]),</span>
      <span class="s2">"— AQI"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">])</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="jp-Cell-outputWrapper">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-OutputCollapser jp-Cell-outputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-OutputArea jp-Cell-outputArea">
<div class="jp-OutputArea-child">
<div class="jp-OutputPrompt jp-OutputArea-prompt"></div>
<div class="jp-RenderedText jp-OutputArea-output" data-mime-type="text/plain" tabindex="0">
<pre>Most polluted year : 2015 — AQI 212.5
Least polluted year: 2020 — AQI 113.5
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=49a7d7c6-bbea-4324-8b75-85761089fdeb">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In [84]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
<div class="cm-editor cm-s-jupyter">
<div class="highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">matplotlib.pyplot</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nn">plt</span>

<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">figure</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">figsize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">))</span>

<span class="c1"># main line</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">plot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">],</span>
         <span class="n">color</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"steelblue"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">linewidth</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">2.5</span><span class="p">,</span>
         <span class="n">marker</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"o"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">markersize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># highlight worst year in red</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">scatter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">],</span>
            <span class="n">color</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"red"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">120</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">zorder</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">annotate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Worst</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s2">"</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">])),</span>
             <span class="n">xy</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]),</span>
             <span class="n">xytext</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.2</span><span class="p">,</span>
                     <span class="n">worst</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">),</span>
             <span class="n">fontsize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">color</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"red"</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># highlight best year in green</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">scatter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">],</span>
            <span class="n">color</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"green"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">120</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">zorder</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">annotate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Best</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s2">"</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">])),</span>
             <span class="n">xy</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]),</span>
             <span class="n">xytext</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.2</span><span class="p">,</span>
                     <span class="n">best</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Average_AQI"</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">),</span>
             <span class="n">fontsize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">color</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"green"</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">title</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Average AQI Across Indian Cities Each Year (2015–2023)"</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">xlabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ylabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Average AQI"</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">xticks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">yearly</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">"Year"</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">astype</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">grid</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"y"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">alpha</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.3</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">tight_layout</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">show</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>
